  "detailed_description": "There is only you, the abandoned remains of a former life and the flourishing nature that feels great in the absence of man. This world is both gloomy and empty, but so incredibly beautiful.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1077520/extras/3d0912e7931596ecae05d4d2a89b2482.poster.avif?t=1732375576\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1077520/extras/3d0912e7931596ecae05d4d2a89b2482.webm?t=1732375576\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1077520/extras/3d0912e7931596ecae05d4d2a89b2482.mp4?t=1732375576\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  <br><br><br>The Light is a remake of the original 2012 game, an atmospheric author’s parable about our place in this world, life and death. Explore a mysterious territory filled with a variety of details that reveal the story. Solve logic puzzles and explore text messages.<br><br>FEATURES<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">    <li>Meditation  first-person  quest<br>    </li><li>Beautiful visual and melodic compositions from Dmitry Nikolaev - the author of OST to the game \"35MM\".<br>    </li><li>A metaphorical philosophical story revealed in a study of details and surroundings.<br>    </li><li>Two endings.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "There is only you, the abandoned remains of a former life and the flourishing nature that feels great in the absence of man. This world is both gloomy and empty, but so incredibly beautiful.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1077520/extras/3d0912e7931596ecae05d4d2a89b2482.poster.avif?t=1732375576\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1077520/extras/3d0912e7931596ecae05d4d2a89b2482.webm?t=1732375576\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1077520/extras/3d0912e7931596ecae05d4d2a89b2482.mp4?t=1732375576\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  <br><br><br>The Light is a remake of the original 2012 game, an atmospheric author’s parable about our place in this world, life and death. Explore a mysterious territory filled with a variety of details that reveal the story. Solve logic puzzles and explore text messages.<br><br>FEATURES<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">    <li>Meditation  first-person  quest<br>    </li><li>Beautiful visual and melodic compositions from Dmitry Nikolaev - the author of OST to the game \"35MM\".<br>    </li><li>A metaphorical philosophical story revealed in a study of details and surroundings.<br>    </li><li>Two endings.</li></ul>",
